metadata.name: Inner Earth#01
metadata.description:
Inner Earth is the first of many upcoming AI mixed with landscape pieces I will be releasing. I have been a photographer for over a decade and more so recently I have discovered a whole new medium of art to portray my creative vision in an otherworldly manner. 

Over the many years I have learned that creativity should not be held back by rules,or bound by a way that society decides we should perceive art. As an artist I have always imagined the world differently in my own unique vision. This has fundamentally shaped the way I choose to present my art.

Now in this new era of digital art/AI art I will also apply the same vision and walk my own path.

This particular piece I call "Inner Earth" is a mixture of both AI art as well as landscape imagery.
